[0.000, "o", "163Hclearly. Start with the purpose, then the architecture, use cases, best practices, and common mistakes. Also, check if there's anything else they might be inter\u001b[71;163Hested in, like specific technologies or configurations.\\n</think>\\n\\nHere's a key summary of reverse proxy best practices and features:\\n\\n### **Reverse Proxy O\u001b[72;163Hverview**\\n- **Purpose**: Handle incoming requests, cache responses, and serve static files.\\n- **Use Cases**: APIs, web applications, caching, and load balanci\u001b[73;163Hng.\\n\\n### \u001b[38;5;247m\u001b[K\u001b[1;74r\u001b[73;174H\u001b(B\u001b[m\u001b[?2026l\u001b[?2026h\u001b[38;5;247m\u001b[48;5;234m\u001b[37;73r\u001b[37;73r\u001b[163;322s\u001b[1;1H\u001b[6S\u001b[37;73r\u001b[s\u001b[67;174H\u001b[32m**Key Features**\\n1. **Architecture**:  \\n   - **Load Balancing**: Distributes traffic across multiple backend servers.  \\n   - **Caching**: Stores s\u001b[68;163Htatic content (e.g., images, CSS) to reduce load and improve performance.  \\n   - **Reverse Proxy as a Gateway**: Directs HTTP requests to backend servers (e.g.\u001b[69;163H, Nginx, HAProxy).  \\n\\n2. **Common Tech"]
[0.000, "o", "nologies**:  \\n   - **Nginx**: Popular for reverse proxying and load balancing.  \\n   - **HAProxy**: For advanced load b\u001b[70;163Halancing.  \\n   - **Apache** or **Vary** headers for dynamic caching.  \\n\\n3. **Best Practices**:  \\n   - Use **reverse proxying** for APIs and static content. \u001b[71;163H \\n   - Implement **Caching** to reduce latency.  \\n   - Use **Load Balancing** to distribute traffic evenly.  \\n   - Monitor performance and optimize configura\u001b[72;163Htions.  \\n\\n### **Common Mistakes**  \\n- Not configuring reverse proxying properly.  \\n- Not caching static files optimally.  \\n- Not using load balancing for h\u001b[73;163High traffic.  \\n\\nLet me know if you need specific configurations or tools!\u001b[38;5;247m\u001b[K\u001b[1;74r\u001b[73;238H\u001b(B\u001b[m\u001b[?2026l\u001b[32m\u001b[48;5;234m 😊\u001b[38;5;247m\u001b[37;73r\u001b[37;73r\u001b[163;322s\u001b[1;1H\u001b[3S\u001b[37;73r\u001b[s\u001b[70;241H\u001b[32m\"\u001b[38;5;247m\u001b[1m,\u001b[71;163H          \u001b[34m\"type\"\u001b[38;5;247m: \u001b(B\u001b[m\u001b[32m\u001b[48;5;234m\"output_text\"\u001b[38;5;247m\u001b[1m,\u001b(B\u001b[m\u001b[38;5;247m\u001b[48;5;234m\u001b[K\u001b[72;163H\u001b[1m          \u001b[34m\"logpr"]
